summary:
I am an Italian/French biotechnology engineer by training, working in life sciences communication & marketing. 
Founder of RPV Consultancy, working as a freelancer, I works in both The Netherlands and Belgium, in different companies with different goals: MEDVIA, a Flemish innovation cluster, supporting collaboration between biotech, MedTech, and digital solutions, Turnstone Communications, a Belgian communication agency, helping sciences companies bringing their innovations into the spotlight, and Hyphen Projects, a Dutch life sciences events company, bridging connections between biotech professionals within the Dutch ecosystem.  

I am also supporting other companies within the life sciences and digital sphere, such as VRforHealth and Sustainable Scale Foundation. 

Awarded by The Next Web (TNW) in 2021 within the ‚ÄúUnder 26 TOP 500 Digital Talents in The Netherlands‚Äù, my ambition is to have impact within the healthcare field all along my career.

Languages that I speak: üá¨üáß üáÆüáπ üá´üá∑
